title.rendered: Day 4. HOUSE OF SKYE presenting SEXYBACK BRA – Miami Swim Week

content.rendered:
Miami Swim Week Powered by Art Hearts Fashion Day 4. 

24Fashion TV Exclusive: 

HOUSE OF SKYE presenting SEXYBACK BRA


HOUSE OF SKYE presenting SEXYBACK BRA showcased a line of versatile statement pieces, fusing high-tech with high fashion with the SEXYBACK BRA.


Photo by Natalie Svors. Exclusively for 24Fashion TV.
